Consequences od Decorator pattern
1. more flexible than static inheritance
2. keeps things simple
3. no practical limit to decorations
4. transparent to clients


Decorator pattern Vs Python decorators(@decorator)
 DP: Implemented with class definitions derived from concrete base class,
        wrap class instance,
        run time decoration
 PD: Implemented with function definitions.
     wrap function or class definitions,
     compile time decoration


